MY VERY FAVORITE MATT DAWSON: I gave my buddy Matt Dawson a copy of Biden Bold a couple weeks back and he came back with some killer Stooges lyrics treatments! The first five treatments above are classic lines from the iconic Detroit proto-punk barracudas. And the next five images are a little collection of the BOSS work that Matt does. Killer moves across the boards! 

Love that heart-shaped record. Love his logo work. Love his  line consistency. Love his Atlanta sorcery. The guy has some serious chops, and, has some serious Crops. Matt‚Äôs the guy behind the mighty @cropcons, which I‚Äôve been lucky to stink up a couple times. Always awesome and loaded with cool people.

Plus, he‚Äôs a husband to the lovely Ariadne, who goes by @staygrayponygirl. Love it. And finally, he looks like Lou Barlow, and I call him a ‚ÄúPoor man‚Äôs Lou Barlow,‚Äù which sounds horrible, but is meant in highest slathering of mushiness. (If you look close in the fifth image, you can see me getting fresh on Matt. Can‚Äôt help it.)

Matt Dawson rips. Plain and simple. And you guys need top follow him, NOW: @staygrayponyboy
